, 2014|df= mdy-all}}</ref>\n| population_note                 = \n| postal_code_type                = [[Canadian postal code|Postal code(s)]]\n| postal_code                     = [[List of H postal codes of Canada|H]] (except H7 for [[Laval, Quebec|Laval]])\n| area_code                       = [[Area codes 514 and 438|514 and 438]] and 263\n| blank_name_sec2                 = GDP\n| blank_info_sec2                 = [[American dollar|US$]]155.9&nbsp;billion<ref name=\"brookingsgdp\">{{cite web |url= http://www.brookings.edu/research/interactives/global-metro-monitor-3 |title= Global city GDP 2014 |publisher= Brookings Institution |accessdate= November 18, 2014 |url-status=dead |archiveurl= https://www.webcitation.org/6H7Jql2A9?url=http://www.brookings.edu/research/interactives/global-metro-monitor-3 |archivedate= June 4, 2013 |df= mdy }}</ref>\n| blank1_name_sec2                = GDP per capita\n| blank1_info_sec2                = US$38,867<ref name=\"brookingsgdp\"/>\n| website                         = {{URL|montreal.ca/en}}\n| footnotes                       = \n| p2                              = [[Anjou, Quebec|Anjou]]\n| p3                              = [[C\u00f4te-des-Neiges\u2013Notre-Dame-de-Gr\u00e2ce]]\n| p4                              = [[L'\u00cele-Bizard\u2013Sainte-Genevi\u00e8ve]]\n| p5                              = [[LaSalle, Quebec|LaSalle]]\n| p6                              = [[Lachine, Quebec|Lachine]]\n| p7                              = [[Le Plateau-Mont-Royal]]\n| p8                              = [[Le Sud-Ouest]]\n| p9                              = [[Mercier\u2013Hochelaga-Maisonneuve]]\n| p10                             = [[Montr\u00e9al-Nord]]\n| p11                             = [[Outremont, Quebec|Outremont]]\n| p12                             = [[Pierrefonds-Roxboro]]\n| p13                             = [[Rivi\u00e8re-des-Prairies\u2013Pointe-aux-Trembles]]\n| p14                             = [[Rosemont\u2013La Petite-Patrie]]\n| 